addLibraryAsLatestMetadataIndexJson - Marks given coordinates as latest in metadata/group/artifact/index.json
addLibraryMetadataIndexJson - Adds given coordinates to metadata/group/artifact/index.json without changing the latest entry
addTestedVersion - Updates list of tested versions.
analyzeExternalLibraryDynamicAccess - Resolves an external Maven coordinate and reports preserve/track dynamic-access totals
checkAllowedDockerImages - Returns list of allowed docker images
checkMetadataFiles - Checks content of metadata files for matching coordinates
contribute - Generates metadata and prepares pull request for contibuting on metadata repository based on provided tests.
discoverArtifactMetadata - Uses a coding agent command to discover artifact metadata for a single coordinate and stores it under build/.
extractLibraryTestParams - Extracts TEST_PATH, LATEST_VERSION and TEST_COORDINATES for given coordinates (group:artifact[:version]). Writes them into GITHUB_ENV.
fetchExistingLibrariesWithNewerVersions - Returns list of all libraries coordinates
fixTestNativeImageRun - Fix test that fails Native Image run for new library version.
generateAffectedSpringTestMatrix - Computes GA changes from git diff, scans Spring AOT for impacted tests, and emits a ready-to-use GitHub Actions matrix.
generateChangedCoordinatesMatrix - Returns matrix definition populated with coordinates of changed libraries
generateChangedCoordinatesOnlyMatrix - Returns a coordinate-only matrix definition populated with changed coordinates
generateChangedIndexFileCoordinatesList - Returns a list of changed coordinates for validation based on git diff
generateChangedMetadataTestMatrix - Returns matrix definition populated with changed coordinates and batched tested versions from metadata index files
generateDependencyGraph - Prints deps.dev dependency graph for matching coordinates
generateDynamicAccessCoverageReport - Generates a per-class dynamic-access coverage report for matching coordinates
generateDynamicAccessReport - Builds native tests and prints generated dynamic-access JSON report files for matching coordinates
generateInfrastructureChangedCoordinatesMatrix - Returns matrix definition populated with pre-selected coordinates when test infrastructure has changed
generateLibraryStats - Generates local library stats and updates stats/<group>/<artifact>/<metadata-version>/stats.json
generateMatrixBatchedCoordinates - Returns matrix definition populated with fractional batch coordinates (k/n)
generateMatrixMatchingCoordinates - Returns matrix definition populated with all matching coordinates
generateMetadata - Generates metadata based on provided tests.
generateNewLibraryVersionCompatibilityMatrix - Returns matrix definition populated with newer library versions and CI environments
generateReadmeBadgeSummary - Generates current README metrics data, coverage Markdown, and updates README metrics history
listCoordinates - Lists all matching GAV coordinates (one per line) honoring -Pcoordinates filter; use -PstrictCoordinates=true for strict matching
listLibraryJars - Lists resolved tested-library JARs for matching coordinates (one per line)
mergeNativeTraceMetadata - Merges runtime metadata trace output directories with native-image-utils generate
populateArtifactURLs - Uses a coding agent command to fill source-code-url, repository-url, test-code-url, documentation-url, description, and language in matching metadata index entries.
pullAllowedDockerImages - Computes and pulls allowed docker images required by matching coordinates
scaffold - Creates a metadata and test scaffold for the given coordindates
splitTestOnlyMetadata - Moves test-only entries from library reachability metadata into test resources metadata.

